# Cloudflare Pages routing.
# Syntax: "from to status".
#
# Cloudflare Pages auto-serves clean URLs from .html files, so:
#   /tier-list         -> tier-list.html
#   /champions/aatrox  -> champions/aatrox.html
#   /builds            -> builds.html
#   /champions         -> champions.html
#   /                  -> index.html
# No explicit rules needed for any of those.

# Legacy redirects: the original coming-soon launch sent everyone to /, so
# any links shared with deep paths during that period need a soft landing.
# (These are safe no-ops once those paths actually exist as real pages.)

# 404 -> the homepage. Cleaner than a generic Cloudflare error page.
/*    /index.html    404
